    "answer_id" : 2444372,
    "question_id" : 2444359,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>You almost always use <code>HashMap</code>, you should only use <code>TreeMap</code> if you need your keys to be in a specific order.</p>\n"
  }, {
